Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.19,0:00:16.66,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Baron...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:22.06,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Baron!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.06,0:00:24.53,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo, staraj sa o deti!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.97,0:00:30.87,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Baron!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.11,0:00:36.11,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Baron?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.11,0:00:38.35,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Bol to sen?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.65,0:00:45.25,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}V 1. dni na svete, pod stromom života,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.25,0:00:51.59,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}dvaja z nás počuli hlasy veľrýb, odrážajúce sa z diaľky.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.59,0:00:57.93,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}So všetkým, čo sme stratili a všetko, čo sme milovali,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.93,0:01:04.61,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}čo sme mali v náručí, kam sa to zatúľalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.61,0:01:10.95,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Odpoveď leží v jantári slnka.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.95,0:01:17.29,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Ak by som ťa nestretla, zničila by som anjela.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.29,0:01:22.89,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Moja duša posadnutá okamihom nesmrteľnosti,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.89,0:01:26.56,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}nezraní moje krídla.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.56,0:01:33.24,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Zrodila som sa, aby som spoznala tento pocit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.24,0:01:39.57,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Po 1.000 rokov a ešte ďalších 2.000, som ťa ľúbila.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.57,0:01:45.91,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Po 8.000 rokoch, som ťa ľúbila ešte viac.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.91,0:01:52.25,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Po ďalších 100.000.000 rokov a ešte ďalších 2.000, ťa budem stále ľúbiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:02:00.79,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Od 1. dňa, keď som ťa spoznala, hudba v mojom pekle nikdy neprestala.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.40,0:02:13.70,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(315,213)\fad(0,200)}"Žiariace tiene"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.47,0:02:14.21,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa deje, Silvia?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.21,0:02:16.08,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Si hore dosť skoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.08,0:02:21.62,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,No... to preto, lebo som mala veľmi zvláštny sen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:23.65,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zvláštny sen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.65,0:02:25.35,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, áno...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.35,0:02:31.56,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,V mojom sne som bola Apollo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.56,0:02:35.66,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Bola si Apollo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.66,0:02:41.14,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Na začiatku,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.14,0:02:46.21,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,som sa sama prechádzala v tmavom lese...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.21,0:02:48.30,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Potom začalo snežiť...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.18,0:02:54.51,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:02:58.72,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Jedz, dieťa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.72,0:03:02.85,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Jedz kým môžeš... to je trik na prežitie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.03,0:03:15.40,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Si vážne ako slnko...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.27,0:03:21.64,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Rozhodnuté! Už viem tvoje meno!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.64,0:03:23.91,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Meno?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.91,0:03:26.28,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Od dneska, si Apollo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.28,0:03:28.82,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Stelesnenie slnka, Apollo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.82,0:03:31.99,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,A... pol... lo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.99,0:03:33.72,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Presne!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.72,0:03:35.89,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.89,0:03:37.22,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:45.47,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,V tvojom sne, dostala si meno Apollo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.47,0:03:47.44,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.44,0:03:55.81,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,A potom som bola s Baronom, špeciálny, vážny, divný a malý.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.81,0:04:01.02,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno... Vedela som dokonca aj ich mená.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.02,0:04:06.25,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Spoločne sme jedli jedlo, ktoré sme dostali.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.25,0:04:09.59,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Boli ste dobrý priatelia, nie?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:14.12,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, áno... A potom sa zrazu objavil.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.14,0:04:22.66,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten bastard, Toma...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.11,0:04:32.18,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Odpusť mi, majster Johannes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:36.17,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nebol som schopný vrátiť pierko uzavreté v jantári.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.69,0:04:42.96,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Bez toho, aby sme zistili, aké informácie uchovávalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.96,0:04:47.29,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Moje schopnosti nestačili.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.16,0:04:54.17,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Strašný omyl jedného, ktorého volajú "Vznešený anjel."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.17,0:04:57.64,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,So všetkou pravdepodobnosťou, tvoj útok bol nedbanlivý
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.64,0:05:00.31,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,kvôli tvojej náklonnosti k tomu zradcovi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.31,0:05:06.08,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, majster Toma nikdy nemal takéto pretrvávajúce city.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.48,0:05:14.09,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak prečo má vyzdobenú prilbu perím toho zradcu Apolloniusa
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.09,0:05:17.39,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,a tak rád ju nosí všade?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:19.39,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to potvrdené...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.39,0:05:24.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,pred 12.000 rokmi, aby sme mali potomkov,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.43,0:05:29.97,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollonius bol vybraný pre svätý čin, ale on ma zradil.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:34.14,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je potvrdené, že som bol hlupák.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.14,0:05:39.88,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph, aké dojemné. Toto sa volá "pretrvávajúca náklonnosť."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:41.85,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Necháme to tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.85,0:05:48.39,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dôležitejšie je, či sa sily Slnečného Krídla plne obnovili?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.39,0:05:50.33,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dovoľte mi odpovedať.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.33,0:05:54.70,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Z toho čo som videl, je ešte slabý
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:59.63,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,oproti tomu, aký bol pred 12.000 rokmi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:05.13,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale určite má sily, o ktorých sme nevedeli.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.14,0:06:10.05,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Avšak, ak Slnečné Krídlo nezhromaždí dosť sily
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:12.98,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,aby oblepil strom života kvetmi
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.98,0:06:18.92,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,a vytvoril ovocie, ktoré dá život novému svetu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.92,0:06:21.72,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak potom je to svätý osud.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.72,0:06:26.46,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak sa tak stane, tak proste zabijem Slnečné Krídlo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.94,0:06:41.81,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Potom, čo sa Toma objavil v mojom sne, tak sa zdalo, že čas skákal dookola.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.41,0:06:51.89,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pred 12.000 rokmi, Apollonius odišiel z môjho života...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:55.46,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Keď som bola malá, môj otec...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.46,0:06:57.89,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Moja mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:07:03.89,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,A teraz aj Baron bol zabitý.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.72,0:07:27.22,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Obaja ste boli veľmi smutní... ty a Apollo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.22,0:07:28.72,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo, tiež?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.72,0:07:33.99,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Snaží sa ako len dokáže, aby prekonal bolesť zo straty blízkeho...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:38.00,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.18,0:07:50.18,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Možno, že intenzita jeho smútku
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:57.08,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,pohla tvojím srdcom a otvorila tvoje sny.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.02,0:08:00.52,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollov sen bol vo mne?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.52,0:08:03.73,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To je hnus!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.73,0:08:05.78,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čokoľvek, len nie toto!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.94,0:08:19.60,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pierka?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:26.78,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo si spomenul na jeho minulý život, nie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.78,0:08:30.85,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Spomienky na Slnečné Krídlo...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.85,0:08:32.52,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako ste vedeli?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.52,0:08:36.49,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Veľa toho viem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.49,0:08:39.79,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Keď sa Apollo vkradol do laboratória,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:42.33,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,tak sa dotkol pierka, ktoré bolo v jantáre, nie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:44.06,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Áno...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.53,0:08:50.60,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Keď sa Apollo dotkol pierka...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:09:02.45,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,A potom sme si spomenuli...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.45,0:09:06.79,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Spomienky Apolloniusa a Seliane.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:11.53,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Chápem... tvoj príbeh je veľmi zaujímavý.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:16.23,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale nemôžeme predpokladať, ako sa Apollo cítil
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.23,0:09:18.57,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,keď zistil skutočnú minulosť.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:19.90,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.90,0:09:26.40,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Obávam sa, že spomienky ľudí, nemusia byť presné.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.74,0:09:32.85,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je možné, že sa falošné myšlienky vytvorili z príbehov, ktoré rozprával
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.85,0:09:36.15,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,zo svätej knihy od vtedy čo prišiel do Deavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.15,0:09:38.82,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Falošné spomienky?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.82,0:09:42.09,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,A tiež, perie Ťieňových Anjelov
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.09,0:09:44.86,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,obsahuje špeciálne sily, o ktorých nič nevieme.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.86,0:09:47.53,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak je možné, že tie informácie spred
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.53,0:09:50.97,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,12.000 rokov, boli nahrané v tom pierku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.97,0:09:54.77,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Obaja ste si proste tú informáciu prečítali.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:10:04.55,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,A Silvia, tiež je možné, že sa Apollo mohol dostať
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.55,0:10:11.32,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,do tvojich myšlienok, a pomýliť si ich so svojimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:15.76,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo? Apollo videl moje spomienky?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:18.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To nemôže byť.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:19.69,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to také nepravdepodobné?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.69,0:10:22.96,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevidela si proste spomienky Apolla vo sne?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:26.47,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,No, ale to je...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.47,0:10:32.01,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Môže to byť každým zjednotením do Aquariona,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.01,0:10:36.21,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,mysle a telá sa prekryjú...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.21,0:10:41.25,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Mohli ste si začať vymienať pocity a myšlienky.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.25,0:10:44.62,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo? Zdielať s ním myšlienky?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:48.89,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nechcem, aby sa to stalo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.89,0:10:54.23,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Možno s bratom, ale nechcem zdielať myšlienky s takou beštiou!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:11:01.17,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale keď ho tak moc nenávidíš, tak prečo sa s ním tak často zjednocuješ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.17,0:11:03.60,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo? To nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:06.41,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to také dobré, že to nemôže byť pravda!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.41,0:11:08.40,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:15.92,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ľudské srdcia sú zložité veci...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.92,0:11:21.16,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie je ľahké pocítiť niekoho pravé pocity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:24.99,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie je ľahké pocítiť niekoho pravé pocity?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.97,0:11:36.54,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aké strašné...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.54,0:11:38.31,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To už zachádza ďaleko...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.31,0:11:39.40,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prichádza!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.75,0:11:44.71,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Kde to je?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:51.75,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Niečo je zle. Nevidím nepriateľa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.75,0:11:53.99,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevidíš?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.99,0:11:57.56,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Verím, že nepriateľ používa optické krytie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.56,0:11:58.93,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Krytie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.93,0:12:00.92,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžeme urobiť nič podobné.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.10,0:12:05.10,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zjednotíme sa a budeme hľadať!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:06.86,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre! Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:17.51,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion Luna!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:32.32,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ukľudni sa... Musím ho nájsť...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.53,0:12:35.59,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prichádza!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.53,0:12:39.66,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Kde je?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.54,0:12:43.97,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Neutečieš!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.85,0:12:54.42,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Bola to atrapa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.42,0:12:56.01,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Návnada?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.82,0:13:02.69,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemáme na výber. Použijeme psychické fotografovanie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:06.39,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Jun Lee, choď do hlavy a nájdi nepriateľa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.39,0:13:09.60,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?! Ja, hlava?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:11.23,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to bezohľadné!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.23,0:13:13.70,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Počul si ho, Jun! Buď muž!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.70,0:13:15.84,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... rozkaz!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.84,0:13:16.77,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nenshin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:17.64,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Gattai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.64,0:13:20.80,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ideš... Ideš! Aquarion!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.12,0:13:28.41,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prichádzam!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:32.78,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aké vzrušenie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.92,0:13:38.33,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion Mars!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:39.52,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zvládol to!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.54,0:13:49.37,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemotorný!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:52.31,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Rýchlo nájdi nepriateľa psychickým fotografovaním!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.31,0:13:53.97,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Rozkaz.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:56.50,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Psychické oko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.85,0:14:02.18,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je blízko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.22,0:14:10.76,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Moc pomalý, Jun. Buď rýchlejší!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.76,0:14:14.46,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Musím ho nájsť... s psychickým fotografovaním...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.76,0:14:18.10,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Jun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.10,0:14:19.77,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Žiadne skúsenosti.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.77,0:14:21.34,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Úbohé!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:23.74,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobrý na nič!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.74,0:14:25.81,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ticho!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.81,0:14:28.21,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Na čo sa pozeráte?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:29.08,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.08,0:14:31.15,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Kde?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.15,0:14:35.02,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Jun nedokáže riadne ani psychicky fotografovať, to je pravda...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.02,0:14:37.69,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja... Ja musím...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.69,0:14:40.12,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale uprostred strachu, nevediac skade zaútočí
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.12,0:14:44.63,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,nepriateľ, ktorého nevidí a je v hlave po 1. krát,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:47.40,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,bojom zosilnený strach a snaží sa nájsť
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:51.16,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,jeho neviditeľného nepriateľa, napriek tomu, že je vydesený na smrť.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.90,0:14:57.54,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevidíte, ako veľmi sa snaží?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.54,0:14:59.71,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Veliteľ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:02.51,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Musím ho nájsť, alebo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.21,0:15:41.45,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Baron...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.45,0:15:43.38,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Baron.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.39,0:15:46.52,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Seliane...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.52,0:15:48.51,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollonius...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.89,0:15:53.22,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Seliane!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:16:02.23,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Jun! Reika-sempai! Pierre-sempai! Odpovedzte!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.97,0:16:09.94,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Bioenergia všetkých elementov klesá! Sú v ohrození.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.94,0:16:14.21,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo robíte? Aký žalostný boj!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.89,0:16:19.89,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Konečne sa prebudil...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.89,0:16:21.92,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Bojuješ za stratené životy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.92,0:16:24.36,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ideme, Seliane!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.36,0:16:25.29,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:28.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo... Práve si povedal Seliane?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.43,0:16:32.47,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prebudil svoj minulý život?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.47,0:16:35.90,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo... bol nahradený inou osobou?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.90,0:16:40.14,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre. Všetci sa vymeňte!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:42.68,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetci sa majú vymeniť?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:46.20,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetci čakajte na výmenu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.26,0:17:05.60,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Genesis Gattai! Ideš!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:07.57,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.98,0:17:19.45,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aké úžasné svetlo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.45,0:17:21.64,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Moc rýchle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.25,0:17:27.39,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ideme, Seliane!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.39,0:17:30.66,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pomstíme Barona!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.66,0:17:32.93,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pomstíme Barona?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.93,0:17:37.16,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Mätie si Apollo jeho minulý život s týmto?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.47,0:17:48.54,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ukľudni sa! Takto nemôžeme nájsť nepriateľa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:49.91,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.91,0:17:52.58,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat... Apollo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.58,0:17:55.72,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ktorý z vás je Slnečné Krídlo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.72,0:17:59.15,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Citová aura elementov Luny vyvinula rozdelenú vlnu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.15,0:18:02.46,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Mám tu veľké zmätky v myšlienkach.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.46,0:18:04.89,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:08.06,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Rýchlo, Seliane! Rýchlo sa musíš ukľudniť!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:11.97,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?! Nerozkazuj mi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.97,0:18:16.17,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak si skutočnou reinkarnáciou Apolloniusa, mal by si byť ku mne milý!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.17,0:18:18.81,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak kto si?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.81,0:18:20.07,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Kto som?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.45,0:18:31.39,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarionove telo je...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.39,0:18:33.55,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Element Sol zmizol!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:35.52,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžem nájsť Apolla.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.52,0:18:37.25,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zmizol?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.03,0:18:43.30,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo... zmizol?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:45.82,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To nemôže byť! Kde je Apollo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:52.37,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To bolo úžasné, majster Toma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.37,0:18:55.38,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vďaka mystickému závoju,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.38,0:19:00.41,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Slnečné Krídlo pocíti strach neviditeľnosti.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:05.05,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Bezkrídli veria iba tomu, čo dokážu vidieť.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.05,0:19:10.12,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,No, čo teraz spravia tie temné duše?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:12.19,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo... kam si zmizol?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.19,0:19:13.73,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.73,0:19:17.30,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemyslíš snáď... že Apollo zomrel?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:23.00,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, ak by Apollo zahynul, zjednotenie by sa rozpadlo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:30.14,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Neviditeľná sila, neviditeľné srdce...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:33.24,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo! Kde si?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.85,0:19:37.18,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.99,0:19:42.46,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Baron!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.36,0:19:46.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nieee!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.43,0:19:48.95,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Baron! Baron!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:53.00,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ukľudni sa, Silvia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.00,0:19:55.97,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz nie je čas na paniku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.97,0:19:59.24,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to do teba vošlo, brat? Nevieš ako sa cítim!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.24,0:20:00.64,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.64,0:20:03.13,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sil... via...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:07.01,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:10.42,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Odpusť mi... Ja... Ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.25,0:20:15.15,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tvoje city?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:20.06,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Moje city sú pre...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.06,0:20:25.73,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie je ľahké pocítiť niekoho pravé pocity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.73,0:20:32.01,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ach môj bože! To znamená, že nedokážem vidieť
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.01,0:20:36.31,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apolla, pretože nedokážem pochopiť vlastné pocity?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.31,0:20:40.78,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je to za zúrivú búrku?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.78,0:20:45.95,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silviin pulz a BP stúpajú! Ak to bude pokračovať, môže to byť nebezpečné.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.52,0:20:52.42,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Moje... pocity...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.91,0:21:15.44,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.86,0:21:25.89,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.89,0:21:40.21,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Som skoro bez dychu zo zázraku nášho stretnutia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.89,0:21:26.53,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:38.84,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Našla si ho?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.21,0:21:41.97,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,V tvojom vlastnom srdci.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.92,0:21:53.79,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Na čo sa pozeráš,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.28,0:21:50.08,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Spravíme to, Silvia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.08,0:21:51.42,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.79,0:22:00.93,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}s tými vždy žiarivými očami?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.79,0:21:55.32,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tu!\N Tu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.93,0:22:11.61,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Som si istá, v tomto svete sa môžeme dotknúť iba my,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.54,0:22:12.77,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Skrýval sa v tieni...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.61,0:22:17.08,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}všetko teraz začne.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.77,0:22:17.08,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To je pravda... v tieni ich srdcí.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.08,0:22:19.05,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(322,159)}"Svetlo a tieň"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.05,0:22:32.29,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Chcela som ti povedať, že som sa narodila, aby som ťa stretla.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.29,0:22:39.63,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Drsný vietor a pohľad, ktorý preniká do môjho srdca,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.63,0:22:49.98,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}všetko sa stalo prenikavým hlasom, vždy po mojom boku.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.98,0:22:56.32,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Zaľúbila som sa do teba
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.32,0:23:03.32,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}S týmto čistým pocitom lásky,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.32,0:23:09.00,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}sa nemusím ohliadať.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.00,0:23:19.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Obaja môžeme lietať navždy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.51,0:23:23.34,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo, toto je pre teba.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.51,0:23:29.04,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ďakujem, Silvia.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.96,0:23:48.27,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Kto povedal, že prvá láska je horká?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.27,0:23:51.84,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak by stál predo mnou, tak by som mu dal...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.84,0:23:54.71,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohnivý gól!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.00,0:24:00.71,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\pos(411,392)}"Prvá láska Aquariona"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.71,0:23:57.21,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nabudúce v Aquarionovi: "Prvá láska Aquariona"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.21,0:23:59.21,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,
